            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p xml:lang="heb">תתניח נפשה<lb/>דעמרן בר יודן <add place="interlinear">דמית</add>
               <lb/>בירח ניסן בעסרה<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">י</supplied>ומין
                    בירחה <space/>
               <lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ב</supplied>שתה שתיתיתה<lb/>
               <supplied reason="lost">ד</supplied>שאבועה דהי <space/>
               <lb/>שנת ארבע מאה<lb/>ותלאתין
                    ותלת שנין<lb/>לחרבן בית מקדשה<lb/>שלום על ישראל</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Rested be the soul<lb/>of 'Amran, son of Yudan, who died<lb/>in the month of
                    Nisan, on the tenth<lb/>day of the month,<lb/>in the sixth year<lb/>of the
                    seven-year cycle which is<lb/>the year four hundred<lb/>and thirty-three
                    years<lb/>of the destruction of the Sanctuary.<lb/>Peace upon Israel.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>דמית omitted by scribe and added in space between lines two and three. Dated to
                    433 E.D.S., 6th S.Y. = 4 April 502 C.E.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
